Comment: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:02.20,IIN,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1640,300)}劇毒
Comment: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.20,IIN,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1640,470)}酩酊
